The fair is broken into sections such as Now!, Influences, Objet (referred to as "the concept store of all concept stores"), Easy Living and Cook &amp; Design, to make it accessible for the 80000-odd visitors who attend. We've sifted through the magic to bring you a roundup of the talent we're most excited to see. - Roberta ThatcherMaison &amp; Objet is on until September 6. Follow @sundaytimeshome_sa on Instagram as Home editor Leana Schoeman posts live from the event. www.maison-objet.com